messages.text: ok, I think you have the wrong number.
how do you know my name?
I don’t even know who this is
what do you expect me to do?
how am I supposed to help
I don’t know what I can do
ok, do you know where you are?
they said you’ll know what it’s about
just tell me what’s going on and I’ll try to help
they said they’ll give you a hint
this is about my debts isn’t it?
did he take you for that?
all they said is only you can save me
tell Jeffy I’ll pay him back
there’s no need to do anything crazy
he’s given you enough time already
just tell him that I can get it to him
can I just talk to him?
he says you have 2 hours to find me
how am I supposed to find you
I don’t even know who you are
they said I can give you hints
until you find the next clue
what am I supposed to look for?
is that where the next clue is?
there’s a bar there called the sunset bar!
“a music box with your next destination inside”
what am I looking for there?
I’ll tell you when you’re there
“a big blue house near the ocean is where your journey ends”
a big blue house near the ocean…
my girlfriend Tessa lives in a big blue house on beryl
then that’s the house you’re looking for
so this was all a lie?
yes. because you lied to me.
that’s what this is all about?
I waited for you to come clean, but you didn’t
so I had to do something extreme
why didn’t you just bring it up
it’s your job to tell me
you could have gotten both of us killed
just give me one more chance
I hope you get everything in order with Jeffy
I just heard car tires screeching outside, was that you?
I can see your car parked, Dave.
if you ever want to see him again you’ll get me what I want
